briefdescription.para: This section describes the API's required to add Hands Free Profile to the user application.

detaileddescription.para: The typical use case for this profile is, a headset wirelessly connected to a mobile phone enabling the user to perform telephone functions through the headset . This library can also connect to an AG supporting HSP only, if the application using this library supports HSP in the SDP.
